SMOOTHIE is a Modern Fortran code for non-elastic breakup calculations in 
inclusive breakup reactions using the formalism of Ichimura, Austern and Vincent.

For more information, visit: https://smoothie.fewbody.com

If you use this software in your research, please cite the following papers:

1. First Numerical Calculation with AHUA Code:
   "Reexamining closed-form formulae for inclusive breakup: Application to deuteron- and ⁶Li-induced reactions"
   Jin Lei and A. M. Moro
   Phys. Rev. C 92, 044616 (2015)
   DOI: 10.1103/PhysRevC.92.044616
   URL: https://journals.aps.org/prc/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevC.92.044616

